<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Urgent Call Request</title>
  </head>
  <body
    style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; padding: 20px;"
  >
    <table
      style="max-width:600px; width:100%; margin:auto; border-collapse: collapse;"
    >
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">
          <h2 style="color: #d9534f;">Hi {{name}},</h2>
          <p>We haven’t heard from you yet, and this first step is too important
            to leave hanging. This call gets us your IRS transcripts, account
            status, and key details that shape how your case moves forward. We
            need your help to help you—without this info, we can’t do the real
            work.</p>
          <p>This won’t be like the IRS calls you’re used to. It’s fast, direct,
            and I’ll be on the line with you the whole way.</p>
          <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-weight: bold;">Call me directly at
            <a
              href="tel:{{phone}}"
              style="color: #d9534f; text-decoration: none;"
            >{{phone}}</a>.</p>
          <div style="margin-top: 40px;">
            {{{signature}}}
          </div>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>